          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Atelier Marinière works through a simple rhythm.<br/>A new collection is released every three months, following the natural pace of the seasons.</p><p><br/>Each collection is available only for a limited period of time. When the access window closes, it does not return.</p><p>Every collection is made in 99 pieces and t<strong>here are no restocks.</strong><br/></p>",
